items.name: case unknown
items.desc: An error code that indicates an unknown error occurred.

items.name: case missingEntitlement
items.desc: An error code that indicates the system extension lacks a required entitlement.

items.name: case unsupportedParentBundleLocation
items.desc: An error code that indicates the extension’s parent app isn’t in a valid location for activation.

items.name: case extensionNotFound
items.desc: An error code that indicates the manager can’t find the system extension.

items.name: case extensionMissingIdentifier
items.desc: An error code that indicates the extension identifier is missing.

items.name: case duplicateExtensionIdentifer
items.desc: An error code that indicates the extension identifier duplicates an existing identifier.

items.name: case unknownExtensionCategory
items.desc: An error code that indicates the extension manager can’t recognize the extension’s category identifier.

items.name: case codeSignatureInvalid
items.desc: An error code that indicates the extension’s signature is invalid.

items.name: case validationFailed
items.desc: An error code that indicates the manager can’t validate the extension.

items.name: case forbiddenBySystemPolicy
items.desc: An error code that indicates the system policy prohibits activating the system extension.

items.name: case requestCanceled
items.desc: An error code that indicates the system extension manager request was canceled.

items.name: case requestSuperseded
items.desc: An error code that indicates the system extension request failed because the system already has a pending request for the same identifier.

items.name: case authorizationRequired
items.desc: An error code that indicates the system was unable to obtain the proper authorization.
